First request a code with this script:

```php
$username = "your phone number including country code without + or 0";
$token = md5($username);
$nickname = "Derp";
$w = new WhatsProt($username, $token, $nickname, true);
$w->requestCode();
```
Then paste the code in this script and let it run:

```php
$username = "your phone number including country code without + or 0";
$token = md5($username);
$nickname = "Derp";
$w = new WhatsProt($username, $token, $nickname, true);
$result = $w->codeRegister("ENTER SMS CODE YOU RECEIVED HERE");
$password = $result->pw;
echo "Password is $password";
```
